# BDA Team CRM Module - Manufacturing Company

## 📌 Project Overview
This project is a MERN-stack based workflow dashboard and CRM module built for the Business Development Associate (BDA) team of a manufacturing company. It helps manage team operations, track leads, and streamline productivity.

## 🚀 Tech Stack Used
* **Frontend:** React.js, Vite
* **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js
* **Database:** MongoDB

## 📂 Repository Structure
All project files and source code are located inside the `bda-crm-project zip.zip` file attached to this repository. Please download and extract the `.zip` file to view the `frontend` and `backend` directories.

